            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/181502783">2009-11-22 16:59:55</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">只要忘记剑心的死，喜欢剑心的就别往下看了。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1440589/?comment_id=181502783"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="731801748">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-731801748" class="vote-count">18</span>
              <a id="btn-731801748" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="731801748">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/smalldie/">smalldie</a>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/731801748">2013-10-03 12:33:51</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">打着工作需要的旗号重新看看。和月伸宏的绘画技巧还是值得肯定的，从始至终都保持了周刊连载漫画流水线作业的较高水平，造型饱满，动态到位，笔法凌厉。故事，还是少年漫画的水平。十多年前看着还挺不错，如今再看就好似白开水了。而且从十多年前开始，我就认定和月伸宏并不是一个苦心孤诣的编剧，后来看访谈和他的自述也得到了印证，所以我对他真是没有热情。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1440589/?comment_id=731801748"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
